             was indicted for <rs id="t18310106-31-off181" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310106-31-off181" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310106-31-off181" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310106-31-cd182" type="crimeDate">17th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310106-31-off181 t18310106-31-cd182"></join>, 46 lbs. weight of rope, value 10s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18310106-31-victim351" type="victimName">
                           George 
                           Lightfoot
                        <interp inst="t18310106-31-victim351" type="surname" value="Lightfoot"></interp>
