            , who had the full charge of the vessel; I saw the rope safe over the long boat's bow on the 16th, when we went to bed - I know nothing of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>GEORGE LIGHTFOOT. I am <rs id="t18310106-31-viclabel184" type="occupation">master of the vessel</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310106-31-victim351 t18310106-31-viclabel184"></join>. This is my rope.</p>
